293
00:29:15,650 --> 00:29:18,310
Ale tu nie je žiadna zodpovedajúca 
adresa.

294
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,800
Nie?

295
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:26,190
Ten dom patrí niekomu inému?

296
00:29:29,760 --> 00:29:31,320
Prosím?

297
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:39,120
