nezabudnem.

345
00:33:28,220 --> 00:33:30,650
Slečna Kim?

346
00:33:33,690 --> 00:33:35,660
Slečna Kim?

347
00:33:56,530 --> 00:33:59,720
Môžete ma odviesť na letisko? 

348
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:05,860
